text: ik's new iRig Keys Pro is the most
compact fullsize midi keyboard
controller on the market in fact it's
30% smaller than any other full-size
midi keyboard controller that can be
played with two hands this shows the
size of iig keys Pro compared to that of
other leading controllers with
full-sized Keys despite its compact
footprint we didn't cut Corners in the
design
iRig Keys pro has 37 fullsize velocity
sensitive keys and is loaded with the
features you need for live performance
jamming and music production you get
pitch and mod wheels and an input for
sustain or expression pedal a built-in
programmable volume data knob makes it
easy to store and send midi control
change and program change
data four backlit soft touch buttons let
you adjust octave up down transpose the
keyboard and even save four Custom
Performance setups you can use iRig Keys
Pro anywhere because it's fully bust
powered it gets its power from the
iPhone iPod Touch iPad or Mac or PC
computer that it's connected to iRig
Keys Pro comes with three different
connection cables including lightning 30
pin and USB so it's good to go with any
iOS device or computer right out of the
box plus you get sample tank free and IG
grand piano free for iOS and Sample tank
L for mac and PC to Kickstart your
creativity iRig Keys is core midi and
USB class compliant which means it's
plug andplay all the way no drivers to
download no complicated configuring just
plug it in and start playing the ultra
compact iRig Keys Pro with fullsize keys
from ik multimedia
